skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Every day, the Unofficial National Day Calendar updates with the national days that you might not know about. Enable this skill to learn what today is. Take your new knowledge and celebrate national days like American Beer Day (10/27), National Two Different Colored Shoes Day (5/3), A’Phabet Day or No “L” Day (12/25), National Teddy Bear Day (9/9), and many, many more!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
